"Mie Gakure" (Belew, Fripp) – 2:00
"She Shudders" (Belew) – 0:35
"Eyes Wide Open" (Belew, Fripp, Gunn, Mastelotto) – 4:08
"Shoganai" (Belew) – 2:53
"I Ran" (Belew) – 0:40
"Potato Pie" (Belew, Fripp, Gunn, Mastelotto) – 5:03
